        public static AnyCControl getCControl(Map node,
                                      boolean search)
        Look for AnyCControl contained as ccControl__ starting at node and progressing to successive parents. If not found then create and store at node or the nearest parent, which must be an AnyFrame and is used as the docking environment's window.
